Class DetailedValidationError

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.esx.settings.clusters.configuration.DetailedValidationError
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.vmware.vapi.bindings.StaticStructure, com.vmware.vapi.bindings.Structure, java.io.Serializable

    public final class DetailedValidationError
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, com.vmware.vapi.bindings.StaticStructure
    The SchemaValidationError class contains details of validation errors for a property. This class was added in vSphere API 8.0.2.0.
